OL,3,GOPINIONCFormat of new STV 6pm news
OL,4,Cprogramme becoming clear
OL,5,
OL,6,FThe format of the new STV News at 6 is
OL,7,Fbecoming clear.
OL,9,FSince Monday, viewers in the north of
OL,10,FScotland have received a programme
OL,11,Fpresented from Glasgow.
OL,13,FMuch of the programme goes out on both
OL,14,FSTV Central and STV North.
OL,16,FThe emerging format seems to be like
OL,17,Fthis:
OL,23,EPub: 15-Jul-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,142,140,200,120,0,100
