OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F141A1784142692
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/4
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCFormat of new STV 6pm news
OL,4,Cprogramme becoming clear
OL,5,
OL,6,F- Separate opening sequences with some
OL,7,Fdistinct headlines. The old opening
OL,8,Ftitles ` which include pictures of
OL,9,Flocations in the STV North area ` have
OL,10,Fbeen retained.
OL,12,F- Around 11 minutes of live Scottish
OL,13,Fnational news.
OL,15,F- A split section which will be
OL,16,Frecorded in one region. This includes
OL,17,Fregional news, the sports desk and the
OL,18,Fweather. I'm guessing it's the opt for
OL,19,Fthe north which will normally be
OL,20,Frecorded.
OL,23,EPub: 15-Jul-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,142,140,200,120,0,100
PN,14103
SC,0003
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F141A1784142692
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G3/4
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCFormat of new STV 6pm news
OL,4,Cprogramme becoming clear
OL,5,
OL,6,F- A second live shared section. This
OL,7,Fincludes banter with the weather
OL,8,Fpresenter and the "and finally" story.
OL,10,FThe sports desk in the north is still
OL,11,Fpresented from Aberdeen although it
OL,12,Falso includes some stories from beyond
OL,13,Fthe STV North area.
OL,15,FAs expected, the branding is unchanged.
OL,17,FAll in all, it's very different to the
OL,18,Fservice from Aberdeen which viewers
OL,19,Fused to get.
OL,23,EPub: 15-Jul-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
