OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F141A1784142692
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G4/4
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCFormat of new STV 6pm news
OL,4,Cprogramme becoming clear
OL,5,
OL,6,FBut it doesn't look or feel very
OL,7,Fdifferent to the programme they got
OL,8,Flast week or last month.
OL,10,FThere is certainly a greater focus on
OL,11,FScottish national stories though.
OL,13,FIt will be worth keeping an eye on the
OL,14,Fnew format to see what happens in the
OL,15,Flonger term.
